description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Plyometric Circuit ' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower and Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Total body work off Hydrow and 2-minute intervals on Hydrow. Explicit lyrics. 

Max rhythm: 24, Format: AMRAP ...
